Definition: the work of making something smooth and shiny by rubbing or waxing it
Example: the shining of shoes provided a meager living; every Sunday he gave his car a good polishing
Synonyms: verb, contact, shine, polishing, polish, work, the, of, making, something, smooth, and, shiny, by, rubbing, or, waxing, it, shoes, provided, a, meager, living, every, Sunday, he, gave, his, car, good
Category: noun.act
